USDT.x (USDTx) is a BEP-20 token deployed on the BNB Smart Chain with a fixed initial supply, optional owner-controlled minting, and built-in 1:1 mint/redeem operations using native BSC USDT (0x55d398326f99059fF775485246999027B3197955).

The token inherits the same decimal precision as BSC USDT for maximum compatibility across DeFi, wallets, and smart-contract integrations.

